    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed per MRL 2 guidance. CFD hemolysis predictions demonstrate normalized RMS error of 9.4% against FDA pump experimental data, and relative hemolysis index RH < 1 is confirmed across all five CPB operating points. The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device within the stated COU.",
